description: AROS Bostadsutveckling AB is a SE-based company operating in Real Estate Management & Development industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2018-11-19. AROS Bostadsutveckling AB is a Sweden-based company, which develops homes mainly in Greater Stockholm and Uppsala. The Company’s business concept is to acquire and develop properties in order to create homes in attractive geographical locations. AROS Bostadsutveckling takes responsibility for the entire housing development process - from the acquisition of land to the handover of a new home in order to ensure quality in homes and processes, as well as security for both buyers and investors.
name: AROS Bostadsutveckling AB
